<item>
            <title>[LU-7304] ldiskfs bug when bigalloc feature enabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7304</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When trying to run benchmarking with bigalloc feature, mkfs always failed&lt;br/&gt;
and dmesg gave following errors:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;LDISKFS-fs error (device sdb): ldiskfs_mb_check_ondisk_bitmap:3611: comm mkdir: on-disk bitmap for group 8corrupted: 0 blocks free in  bitmap, 32768 - in gd&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Centos7</environment>
